		<span id="title-175712351" class="story-title"> <a   href="//hardware.slashdot.org/story/24/12/20/1755236/us-data-center-power-use-could-nearly-triple-by-2028-doe-backed-report-says">US Data-Center Power Use Could Nearly Triple By 2028, DOE-Backed Report Says</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-data-center-power-use-could-nearly-triple-by-2028-doe-backed-report-says-2024-12-20/"  title="External link - https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-data-center-power-use-could-nearly-triple-by-2028-doe-backed-report-says-2024-12-20/" target="_blank"> (reuters.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
